            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Patern</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Aprili&amp;lt;u&amp;gt;s <lb n="4"/>Cresc&amp;lt;e&amp;gt;ns <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden zusammen mit Teilen einer Jupitersäule. Auf den Nebenseiten Darstellung des Saturn und eines Genius. (B): Goeßler, AE 1932: Z. 2: Paterni(us); Z. 4: Crescens; Kortüm: Z. 2: Patern(ii). Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
